The URL for the remote server is :

https://rps.cscvr.umassd.edu:8000

This is accessible from off-campus. Please note that there is a glitch
on the server side. When first logging on, your home directory has not
yet been created. So you may need to log on, log off, quit your browser, 
wait a few minutes, and then log on again. After this, all should work
seamlessly.
